---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Usage — LexiAtlas">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1 style="margin-top:0">Usage, rights, and takedown</h1>
      <p>
        This project aims to preserve and improve a useful directory of language-learning resources.
        Some material was reconstructed from archived pages, and we’re actively maintaining and updating it.
      </p>
      <h2>Provenance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>V1 content began as a reconstruction from archived pages (Wayback Machine), then was imported into this site.</li>
        <li>Over time, content is corrected, expanded, and reorganized; we aim to document major changes.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Attribution</h2>
      <p>
        We intend to credit the original creator prominently. If you know the correct attribution details, please contact us.
      </p>
      <h2>Takedown / corrections</h2>
      <p>
        If you are the original creator, represent the rights holder, or believe content should be removed or corrected,
        please contact the maintainers. Include the specific page URL(s) and what you’d like changed.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>If you can, include proof of authorship/rights (even minimal context helps).</li>
        <li>We’ll respond and, when appropriate, remove or revise content promptly while we sort out provenance.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="muted">
        Link updates and corrections: use <a href="/contribute/">Contribute</a> (preferred) or email <a href="mailto:admin@lexiatlas.org">admin@lexiatlas.org</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

